---
import { brands } from '@/data/company';
---

<section id="estructura-corporativa" class="py-20 bg-brand-cream scroll-mt-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 justify-center mb-4">
        <div class="h-px w-8 bg-brand-green"></div>
        <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-green"></div>
        <div class="h-px w-8 bg-brand-green"></div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-brand-dark mb-3">
        Estructura Corporativa y Marcas
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Un ecosistema de marcas diseñado para operar en distintos mercados con una sola identidad de calidad y confianza.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Corporate diagram -->
    <div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
      <div class="bg-brand-dark text-white rounded-2xl px-8 py-4 text-center">
        <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-white/50 mb-1">Casa Matriz</div>
        <div class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-green">ASOPROARUZI</div>
        <div class="text-white/60 text-xs">Ecuador</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Connection line -->
    <div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
      <div class="w-px h-8 bg-brand-green/40"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Brands grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      {brands.map(brand => (
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 group relative overflow-hidden">
          <!-- Top accent -->
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1" style={`background-color: ${brand.color}`}></div>
          
          <!-- Flag / icon -->
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">{brand.icon}</div>
          
          <!-- Brand name -->
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-dark mb-1 group-hover:text-brand-green transition-colors">
            {brand.name}
          </h3>
          
          <!-- Tagline -->
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 pb-4 border-b border-gray-100">
            {brand.tagline}
          </p>
          
          <!-- Description -->
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            {brand.description}
          </p>

          <!-- Country badge -->
          <div class="mt-5 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
            <span class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-400">
              📍 {brand.country}
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Note -->
    <div class="mt-10 text-center">
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm max-w-lg mx-auto">
        Cada marca opera de forma especializada en su mercado, respaldada por la solidez institucional y la experiencia de Asoproaruzi.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
